file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: OpenAPI definition
  version: v0
servers:
- url: localhost
  description: ' Default server url'
paths:
  /user:
    get:
      operationId: modelClass
      parameters:
      - name: query
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        x-param-extra:
        - name: id
          type: String
          format: ^KW-[0-9]{4}$
          example: id:KW-1234
        - name: keyword_id
          type: String
          format: ^KW-[0-9]{4}$
          example: keyword_id:KW-1234
        - name: name
          type: String
          format: Free text
          example: name:protein
        - name: ancestor
          type: String
          format: Free text
          example: ancestor:protein
        - name: parent
          type: String
          format: Free text
          example: parent:protein
      - name: fields
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        x-param-extra:
        - name: id
          optional: "false"
        - name: keyword
          optional: "false"
        - name: description
          optional: "true"
        - name: category
          optional: "true"
        - name: synonym
          optional: "true"
        - name: gene_ontology
          optional: "true"
        - name: sites
          optional: "true"
        - name: children
          optional: "true"
        - name: parent
          optional: "true"
        - name: statistics
          optional: "true"
      - name: sort
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
        x-param-extra:
        - name: name_sort
          example: name_sort asc
      - name: otherField
        in: query
        schema:
          type: string
      - name: size
        in: query
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      responses:
        200:
          description: default response
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ModelClass'
components:
  schemas:
    ModelClass:
      type: object
